---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import logo from '../content/logo.png';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';

---
<Layout title="Paradigm Engineering">
	<div class="relative w-full">
		<div class="w-full h-2/3 bg-[url('/header-2.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
			<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center pt-[20vh] pb-[10vh]">
				<div class="h-1/4 flex w-[60vw] items-center flex-col 2xl:text-start text-center bg-black bg-opacity-50">
					<div class="w-full self-stretch text-center text-white font-anta text-[2rem] md:text-[4rem] sm:text-[3rem]">SPONSOR PARADIGM</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="who" class="flex justify-center bg-white">
		<div class="w-2/3 flex flex-col items-center py-[10vh]">
			<div class="text-2xl font-roboto">Why Sponsor Paradigm?</div>
			<hr class="w-16 h-0.5 my-2 border-0 bg-gray-900">
			<div class="pt-4 text-gray-700">
Appeal to potential sponsors with importance of funding for team activities. How does being a part of Paradigm change the experience of being an engineering student at mun?
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="what" class="w-100 flex justify-center bg-gray-200">
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center py-10">
			<div class="text-2xl font-roboto">Sponsorhip Package</div>
			<div class="pt-4 text-gray-700">
Read more about becoming a Paradigm sponsor in our sponsorship package here.			</div>
			<iframe class="h-screen 2xl:w-[50%] w-[85%] py-5 xl:block hidden" src="/Sponsorship-Package-3.pdf" allow="autoplay"></iframe>
			<Button buttonText="Download" href="/Sponsorship-Package-3.pdf"/>
		</div>
	</div>
	
		
	</div>
</Layout>
